sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant VAR as VA Reconciler
    participant CMR as ConfigMap Reconciler
    participant SatEng as Saturation Engine<br/>30s polling
    participant SFZEng as Scale-From-Zero Engine<br/>100ms polling
    participant Cache as Decision Cache<br/>(in-memory)
    participant Prom as Prometheus / Thanos<br/>9091/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant EPP as EPP Pods<br/>HTTPS TLS
    participant Actuator as Actuator
    participant Metrics as /metrics endpoint<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant HPA as HPA / KEDA
    participant Workload as Deployment / LWS<br/>(vLLM servers)

    Note over User,Workload: Flow 1: Saturation-Based Autoscaling Loop

    User->>K8s: Create VariantAutoscaling CR
    K8s-->>VAR: Watch event (VA created)
    K8s-->>CMR: Watch event (ConfigMap)
    CMR-->>SatEng: Apply config (thresholds, analyzer)

    loop Every 30 seconds
        SatEng->>Prom: PromQL: kv_cache_usage_perc,<br/>num_requests_waiting, cache_config_info<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
        Prom-->>SatEng: vLLM metrics response
        SatEng->>SatEng: Run analyzer (V1/V2/Queueing)
        SatEng->>Cache: Store VariantDecision
        Cache->>VAR: GenericEvent trigger
        VAR->>K8s: Patch VA status<br/>Auth: SA token
        VAR->>Actuator: Emit scaling decision
        Actuator->>Metrics: Update wva_desired_replicas,<br/>wva_desired_ratio
    end

    Prom->>Metrics: Scrape /metrics<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    HPA->>Prom: Query wva_desired_ratio<br/>Auth: SA token
    HPA->>K8s: Scale Deployment/LWS<br/>Auth: SA token
    K8s->>Workload: Update replicas

    Note over User,Workload: Flow 2: Scale-From-Zero Detection

    loop Every 100ms
        SFZEng->>EPP: GET flow_control_queue_size<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (EPP metrics token)
        EPP-->>SFZEng: Queue metrics response
        alt Pending requests for idle variant (replicas=0)
            SFZEng->>K8s: Scale subresource 0→1<br/>Auth: SA token
            K8s->>Workload: Create first replica
            SFZEng->>Cache: Store decision + trigger
            Cache->>VAR: GenericEvent trigger
        end
    end
